### Booking ###

### Obtener todos los bookings
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### Obtener un booking por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/2
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### Crear un nuevo booking
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "date": "2025-07-15T10:00:00.000Z",
  "customerId": 2,
